Tire Kan x Kamiusagi Rope: A collaboration between Kamiusagi Rope and Tire Kan, an automotive supply store focused on tires owned by Bridgestone. This entry includes the episodes as well as unique commercials. The commercials were shown on TV and on the web while the episodes were web-only.
